      <akn:section eId="sec_2_1801_04">
        <akn:num>2-1801.04</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Monetary sanctions.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_2-1801_04_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p></akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_2-1801_04_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>In addition to any civil fines and penalties imposed following the adjudication of an infraction adverse to a respondent, an administrative law judge or attorney examiner may, in accordance with rules issued by the Mayor, impose upon the respondent, by order, the costs to the District of any additional inspections before, during, or after the hearing, and other costs associated with the hearing.</akn:p></akn:content>
